  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ObjectName: Selection Tool - Rotate, Re-align, duplicate, etc.
  objectTips:
  - Make sure to hold shift or alt while dragging with C.
  - Right Click while dragging/rotating to cancel
  - Press ctrl + D to duplicate selected objects
  - You can directly select objects underneath objects that are already selected.
  - When editing object rotation properties (x z y)... Beware of "gimbal lock"
